<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Upturn</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include ../partials/_menu %>
  <main class="wrapper case-study upturn">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Upturn</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Let your great work&nbsp;<br />do the talking</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Brand System &amp; Publishing Platform</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We created two brand systems and platforms that showcase the great minds, work, and content from the Upturn team.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded dark-blue">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Make it clear and simple.
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Upturn needed a brand system that made their work&mdash;in law and technology&mdash;friendly and accessible, just like they are.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Friendly, modern, and fresh
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We kept the tone and visual direction lighthearted and simple, letting Upturn’s personality shine.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Brand System</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Front-end Development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md light-blue">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="680" data-height="584">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/upturn-logo.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image full-height sr-bottom">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block hide-overflow column half-md">
        <div class="inner-box light-gray">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="680" data-height="293">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/upturn-icons.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-box dark-blue">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="680" data-height="293">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/upturn-half-blocks.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-right">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top light-gray">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right padded-bottom">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Turn the swag on.</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Subtle animations call attention to the most important points of the content for Upturn’s platform, keeping the user’s interest. Sometimes it’s the details&mdash;dropping in custom project icons or just passing clouds&mdash;that take an interface from average to exemplary.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-bottom half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop darker shadow edge-bottom sr-bottom lazy-ratio" data-width="1369" data-height="1709">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/upturn-home.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/upturn-cards.svg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="inner-block gutter-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Brands that play together stay together.</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We built a second, complementary brand system and website to support Upturn’s online publication, Equal Future. This platform maintains its own content and identity, but shares the same accessible tone that makes them stand out in the space.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md">
        <div class="inner-box light-gray">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="681" data-height="293">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/eq-future-full-logo.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-box gray">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="681" data-height="293">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/eq-future-logo-minis.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-right">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column half-md orange">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="678" data-height="584">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/eq-future-logo.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image full-height sr-reveal">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded light-gray">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="inner-block-content">
              <h2 class="case-block-heading">Amazing content that is easy to read.</h2>
              <p class="case-block-text">
                The content on Equal Future analyzes complex policy issues, making them simpler for readers. We did our part, making this great content easier to read and digest, using comfortable spacing, margins, and custom visual elements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md two-third-lg half-xl gutter-left-mobile upturn-content">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop darker shadow edge-right sr-right lazy-ratio" data-width="1135" data-height="671">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/eq-future-desktop.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile darker shadow absolute-bottom sr-bottom">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/eq-future-mobile.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block light-gray">
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop darker shadow sr-tall edge-bottom lazy-ratio" data-width="1030" data-height="845">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upturn/eq-future-post.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral centered row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column dark-gray">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text centered">&ldquo;When we started, I thought the main impact of branding and design work would be to change how other people saw our work. The part I didn't foresee was that beautiful design, when taken to this level, also shapes the way we see ourselves. There's something inspiring about knowing how great our work can look. It's going to help us bring our best writing and thinking to the table.&rdquo;</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">David Robinson, <em>Principal, Upturn</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/cityhealth" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
        <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
        <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
      </div>
      <a href="./work/fieldone" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
    </section>

    <%- include ../partials/_footer %>
  </main>

  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
